data.description: Welcome to this home located in Flint, TX! Enjoy the convenience of living in a neighborhood, but with country views. This home has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and approx. 1505 SF. An open-concept floor plan, great size family room with corner gas fireplace, and a kitchen-eating area. The kitchen features plenty of cabinets and countertop space, breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances, and pantry. Primary suite split has walk-in closet, double sinks, shower with glass door, a large garden tub, and an additional walk-in closet. The extra bedrooms are good sizes, offering plenty of space. Utility room that has above built-in cabinets. Backyard is ideal for entertaining and relaxing that include a pergola with concrete patio and completely fenced. Make this your next home...
